	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Legi, quae scribebas, frater, de tractatione mea etc. ac ago gratias domino deo meo, qui per me in lucem dedit, quae viri pii et docti non improbant, in quorum numero te colloco non inter postremos.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi vero ab <persName ref="p8126" cert="high">Oporino</persName> d. <persName type="auto_name">Boquini</persName> et d. <persName ref="p8115" cert="high">Pincieri</persName> et d. d. <persName type="auto_name">Wolphgangi Germanicum</persName> librum de coena.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam mutarint sententiam senatores!</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non parum offendentur illustrissimi principes d. <persName type="auto_name">Palatinus</persName> et <persName type="auto_name">Hessus</persName> etc.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum audio <persName ref="p3099" cert="high">Sulcerum</persName> et nescio quem <persName type="citizen_name">Coccium</persName> [vel] <persName type="citizen_name">Essich</persName> pluris facere <placeName ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtembergensem</placeName> principem et <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentium</persName> quam suas ipsorum ecclesias et pios omnes.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nescio tamen, an hi in culpa sint; scribitur ad nos istos vehementer esse suspectos.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Certe ubi Lutherani sunt, ibi turbas movent etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus convertat eos aut subvertat prava et irrequieta eorum consilia!</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ago tamen gratias tuae humanitati, qui libellos illos mittere volueras, si caruissem.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eadem vero <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1754">Iungius</persName> noster ad me scripsit, quae ad te.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caeterum post factum interrogas de literis in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Angliam</placeName> commode mittendis; mittimus enim per mercatores <placeName ref="l157" cert="high">Francfordiam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed et hinc discessit d. <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name">Iulius</persName>, <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Martyris</persName> minister, in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliam</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Forte ad mercatum <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinensem</placeName> commode mittes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si item <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinam</placeName> miseris nunc ad d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8121" cert="high">Christophorum Montium</persName> doctorem, <persName type="citizen_name">reginae Angliae</persName> secretarium, et oraveris, ut is curet, libenter recipiet pro sua humanitate; saepius enim ad ipsum literas mitto, at ante discessum mercatorum misi, quae volui etc.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vereor socios aut foederatos nostros externa inopia oppressos, impios item crudeles et a papa absque intermissione ad bellum instigatos mala tentare consilia.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus misereatur nostri et convertat illos vel evertat truculenta consilia aut, si pro meritis nostris incusserit ferulam, non in furore suo nos arguat!</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quia nihil omnino te habere audio eorum, quae <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1811">Naumburgi</placeName> tractata sunt, mitto quaedam de concilio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentino</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rogo autem, ut remittas in tempore curesque, ne amittantur; <foreign xml:lang="de">uffs lengst biß frytag schickents wider.</foreign></s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Communica cum d. <persName type="auto_name">Matthia</persName>, quem salutabis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguri</placeName> 28. martii 1561.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich bitten, ir wöllind dises gen <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l50" cert="high">Bischoffzell</placeName> fertigen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Lutherani prorsus evertunt ecclesias in dominatu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l411" cert="high">Rychevillano</placeName>; <foreign xml:lang="de">es muͦß alles gan nach der Wirtenberger reformation etc.</foreign></s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName>, Vituduri agenti, domino suo colendissimo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wintherdur.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
